HEADWORD: peacetime
<hw>peacetime</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A period of time during which
there is no war; <as>as, civil liberties are valued more highly in
<ex>peacetime</ex> than in war</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

